tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  14,49,"(Thou wilt see the guilty) the idolaters (on that day) the Day of Judgement (linked together in chains) with the satans."
  14,51,"They emerge and become manifest to Allah so (That Allah may repay each soul) whether it is a believing or a sinful soul (what it hath earned) of good or evil. (Lo! Allah is swift at reckoning) Allah is severe in His chastisement."